Rowdy Wolf:








Breaking his walk, Rowdy Wolf turned into a trot, entering his cave. Inside 
was just the same as he left it, as it usually was. The stopped and turned 
his broad head towards Zyber.

"I'm begining to like company than being alone all the time." He tilted his 
head to the side with a slight grin on his muzzle. "It's someone to talk 
to."
